{"name":"Shoot","type":"feat","img":"icons/weapons/guns/rifle-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x1 (Physical)<br />Careful: If you also use your minor action this Attack is made with Boon +2. If you used the Aim Ability before using Shoot, you make this attack with Boon +4 instead.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 5 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A basic ranged attack. This can be shooting a bow, firing a gun, throwing a dagger or dart, shooting spines, and so on.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"long"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":1},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466379081,"modifiedTime":1670974920922,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"6WYWuE3gdWESzSqZ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Remedy","type":"feat","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-conical-corked-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: Reduce the duration of one Status Ailment the target is suffering from by 3 rounds.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 4 MP to increase reduce a Status Ailment's duration by 5 round, or reduce two different Status Ailment durations by 3 each. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A maneuver that removes a lingering difficulty from an ally. This could be a healing spell, a quick repair job on the target's equipment, mundane medical interventions, or similar efforts.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"aux","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466111602,"modifiedTime":1670974920917,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"9RBohVAC2EKpGs46","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Double Strike","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/strikes-sword-scimitar.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x1 (Physical)<br />Effect: When you use this Attack, you make two Offense rolls and resolve them separately. You may strike one enemy twice or two enemies once.<br />Description: A pair of quick strikes. This could be striking with a pair of daggers, swiping with two claws, a small flurry of kicks, swiping back and forth with a hatchet, and similar multistrikes.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":2,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668393361728,"modifiedTime":1670974920890,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"Bs7RoaHhyVA2t4eU","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Scan","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/perception/orb-crystal-ball-scrying-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Careful: Cost reduces to 0 MP</p><p>Effect: You immediately learn the target’s elemental properties, Physical and Mental Defense, ongoing effects (such as buffs or injuries), and their remaining HP.<br />If you spend your major action while using this Ability, you remove the MP cost entirely.<br />Alternatively, Scan can be used on a Square. Scanning a Square reveals the presence of invisible creatures or objects, though it does not reveal their exact location unless they are using an Ability canceled by Scan, such as Vanish.<br />You can use this outside of combat, but you must succeed on a Stealth or Deception roll against the opponent’s Awareness or Empathy roll to remain undetected. The Arbiter will choose which rolls to use based on the situation and may make the rolls secretly. On a failure, the target will become aware that you are sizing them up for combat, which may be interpreted as a hostile action. If you used the Careful action, this check to avoid detection is made with Boon +3.<br />Description: The most basic information gathering ability. Depending on the situation this can represent scanning the target with a power reader, minor mind reading to learn the target’s fears, careful evaluation using mundane senses, or similar actions.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"minor","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"space"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"long"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":1},"ability":null,"actionType":"aux","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7d2xIHVnKyWMImHK"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"#{VERSION}#","coreVersion":"10.303","createdTime":1668466318993,"modifiedTime":1692734266837,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3},"_id":"Cou1qOUDc10cj9dp"}
{"name":"Sneak Attack","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-dagger-blood-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x3 (Physical)<br />Effect: This Attack can only be used on a Flat Footed target.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 7 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A cheap shot at an opponent who is not ready. This could be a thrown dagger, setting off a sneakily place trap, a sucker punch, or anything similar.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":"Enemy is Flat Footed"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"short"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":4},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x3 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466532656,"modifiedTime":1670974920924,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"F9ivKbE7SaUdA2Ga","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
