{"name":"Protector's Presence","type":"feat","img":"icons/environment/people/infantry-army.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: You gain Taunt.<br />Description: You provide cover for nearby allies. This can be physically standing between them and danger, yelling or making noise so that enemies pay attention to you, or similar actions.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"minor","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"none"},"upkeep":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":null,"amount":1},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":1},"ability":null,"actionType":"aux","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668465866847,"modifiedTime":1670974920913,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"G9pDXQ0OxcK1xY1y","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Heavy Strike","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-hammer-destructive-orange.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x2 (Physical)<br />Effect: If you land a Solid Hit, you knock your target Prone.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 6 HP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A strong melee attack. This can just be a particularly powerful uppercut or roundhouse kick, grasping a weapon with both hands while swinging recklessly, a crushing bite, and so on.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"hp","target":"attributes.hp.value","amount":3},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x2 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668465569150,"modifiedTime":1670974920907,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"GG0AHat22FI9FZob","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Vanish","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/movement/trail-streak-impact-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: You are Obscured for the duration. If you are targeted by Scan or use an Ability that targets an opponent, this Ability ends.<br />When you use this Ability, you may also move 1 Square and/or make a Stealth roll opposed by your opponents' Awareness rolls. Anyone who fails this roll does not know your position until you are revealed and cannot target you with single target Abilities. Anyone who does knows what Square you are in, though you remain Obscured to them.<br />If you attack an opponent who is not aware of your location, you may treat them as Flat Footed.<br />Description: Vanishing suddenly in combat. This could be throwing down a smoke bomb, an invisibility spell, activating a cloaking device, or just being really sneaky.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"spec"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"none"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":5},"ability":null,"actionType":"aux","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":3,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466789999,"modifiedTime":1670974920931,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"GgGZNA2abqbucojf","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Veil","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/air/air-smoke-casting.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: The targeted Square becomes impossible to see through for the duration. Targets inside the Square are Blinded and Obscured.<br />Description: An easy way of limiting enemy vision (though allies are similarly hindered). This could be throwing a smoke grenade, conjuring a thick fog, lighting an alchemical concoction that produces thick smoke, and other similar effects that obscure vision.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"minor","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":3,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"space"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"short"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":4},"ability":null,"actionType":"aux","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466853839,"modifiedTime":1670974920932,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"H0pGWMaRI2I4PizB","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Cleanse","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/holy/prayer-hands-glowing-yellow.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: Choose one of the following:</p><ul><li>Increase the target along one Buff Track of your choice by two. You can only increase the value up to 0.</li><li>Increase the target along both Buff Tracks by one. You can only increase the value up to 0.</li><li><p>End a Curse effect on the target.</p></li></ul><p><br />Description: The most basic way to recover from ill effects. This could be magically banishing the curse in question, applying medicine to reverse negative effects, utilizing nanobots to repair the target’s damage, or similar things.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"minor","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"short"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"aux","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.6fClXd0X5T082haZ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.7.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668393045057,"modifiedTime":1672693418356,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3},"_id":"JrARKy566QHzwERG"}
{"name":"Healing Burst","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-area-circle-red-green.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: You and all allies in the same Square regain HP equal to a ten-sided die roll.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 8 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A burst of healing energy that heals all allies in a small area. This can be a few notes in a rousing song, a blast of healing light, channeling energy from enslaved spirits into your allies, a release of medical nano-bots, and similar ways of healing friends in an area.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"space"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":5},"ability":null,"actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["d10","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Healing Touch | Healing Word"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668465359577,"modifiedTime":1670974920903,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"KPIR0pey80LWicsZ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
