{"name":"Kinetic Pummeling","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/ranged/tracers-triple-orange.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Careful: If you spend your minor action while using this Ability, the MP cost is reduced by 2.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 8 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability, and using your Careful action reduces the cost by 3.<br />Description: A basic area of effect kinetic spell. This could represent an unfocused wave of psychic energy, telekinetically picking up and hurling many small projectiles in an area, scatter-shot weapons like shotguns or sub-machine guns, and the like.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"space"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":6},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Kinetic Dart & Kinetic Force"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668465711184,"modifiedTime":1670974920911,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"QBSVsrQHrnv3gOCp","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Grapple","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/unarmed-punch-fist.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: If this Attack succeeds, you also Grab the target.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 5 HP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability. The cost increase only affects the initial use of the Ability; its Upkeep is unchanged.<br />Description: Moving in to grapple with foes. Unlike Tier 0’s Grab, this represents someone with skill and training making the attempt. This could represent a skilled wrestler’s grab, a disciplined takedown, jujutsu locks, or the like.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"attribute","label":"hp","target":null,"amount":1},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":3},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668448537183,"modifiedTime":1670974920901,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"SI8fe77b8yixLIWx","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Dodge","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/movement/feet-winged-boots-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: Reduce the Impact of the successful Ability by 3. This reduces the damage you take. This can turn a normal hit into a miss, reduce a Solid Hit to a normal hit, or a Critical Hit into a Solid Hit.<br />Description: A last minute reaction that allows one to just barely dodge an incoming attack.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"counter","cost":0,"condition":"Hit by Enemy Ability"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"none"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"aux","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.9.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668393307808,"modifiedTime":1683010387095,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"TjsN16LnQaD6b1Gv","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Throw","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/unarmed-punch-fist-yellow-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: You must have grabbed one of your targets. Make a single Offense roll against both enemies. If you score a hit, you knock the target Prone as well as doing damage. After using this Attack, you are no longer grabbing your original target.<br />Description: Tossing your grappled foe into one of their allies. This could be bodily picking up and tossing them, controlling their momentum in a way that causes them to fly into each other, or something similar.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":"Enemy is Grabbed"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":2,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":3},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Grapple"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466744991,"modifiedTime":1670974920929,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"Vazx22ZuD2Koe5MY","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Enfeeble","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/unholy/projectile-smoke-trail-pink.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: If you hit, the target decreases on the Offensive Track.<br />You may use this either as an Attack (using your Physical Offense and targeting your opponent’s Physical Defense) or a Spell (using your Mental Offense to target you’re opponent’s Mental Defense).<br />Scaling: At any Hero Tier, you may increase the cost of thie Ability by 7 MP to give it a damage multiplier of 1.<br />At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by an additional 8 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A simple ability to make a target less effective offensively. This could be a curse, distracting or discouraging the target, sapping their strength away, hampering their vision, adjusting gravity around them to make their weapons and gear more unwieldy, and other things to hinder the target.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: 0","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.glyTd9sHBZzdYrEL"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.7.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668393653151,"modifiedTime":1672693508785,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3},"_