{"name":"Mobile Strike","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-steel-yellow.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: You may move one Square before or after you make your Offense roll.</p><p>Description: A mobile strike. This could be a lunging charge, kicking off an enemy to make space as part of your attack, attacking after teleporting a short distance, or some other maneuver where an attack is paired with movement.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Double Strike"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668465822203,"modifiedTime":1670974920912,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"d3tKctfOzIsmvWAs","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Bash","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/shield-block-bash-yellow.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x1 (Physical)<br />Effect: If this Attack scores a Solid Hit and the target is not otherwise restrained, you move them one Square.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 4 HP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A strike so powerful that it sends opponents sprawling backward. This could be a body slam, a shield bash, beating them backwards with wind from your wings, and similar attacks.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"hp","target":"attributes.hp.value","amount":3},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668392891385,"modifiedTime":1670974920880,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"d6gf1egNGlYUGItv","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Snapshot","type":"feat","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x1 (Physical)<br />Cooldown: 1 round<br />Description: A quick ranged attack. This could represent throwing a hidden dagger, shooting an off-hand pistol, or in combination with Shoot might represent notching and firing two arrows from a bow at once, or activating a weapon's burst fire mode.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"minor","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":1,"charged":false},"requirements":"Shoot"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466479064,"modifiedTime":1670974920923,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"dDhBWXAtplTWdvX8","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Decelerate","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/movement/chevrons-down-yellow.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: If this Spell hits, the target is Slowed for 2 rounds. If this Spell scores a Solid Hit, the Slow lasts for 3 rounds. If it scores a Critical Hit, the Slow lasts for 4 rounds.<br />Description: Hindering your foe's freedom of movement. This could represent time magic, activating a restraining device, increasing the pull of gravity for the target, or similar measures.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":3},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: 0","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668393187604,"modifiedTime":1670974920887,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"eHteBou18MYUMzId","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Demand","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/sonic/scream-wail-shout-teal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: You may used your Physical or Mental Offense on this Ability. If you use Physical Offense, treat this Ability as an Attack. If you use Mental Offense, treat this Ability as a Spell.<br />If this Ability hits the target, they are Provoked by you for one Round.<br />You may choose to use your Defense Bonus instead of your Offense for this Ability.<br />Description: Drawing an opponent's attention. This could be shouting insults or making noise, subtle mind control, magically drawing bullets toward oneself, or otherwise force opponents to focus on you.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"minor","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"long"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":1},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: 0","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668393227298,"modifiedTime":1670974920888,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"fuSJhGy797ErA33n","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Healing Touch","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-hand-gold-green.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: The target regains HP equal to a ten-sided die roll.<br />This Ability may only be used once per Turn.<br />Scaling: At any Hero Tier, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 4 MP to add another ten-sided die to the amount healed.<br />At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by an additional 6 MP to add another ten-sided to the amount healed for a total of 3d10. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A quick healing ability that must be done up close. This could be jamming a syringe into the target, applying a healing herb, channeling vitality through your hands, and other similar actions.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"minor","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":3},"ability":null,"actionType":"heal","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["d10","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668465439979,"modifiedTime":1670974920905,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"gqPGS89bdFnqiM6P","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Elemental Lance","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/lightning/strike-arrow-spear-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x1 (Fire/Ice/Earth/Sky/Light/Dark)<br />Special: When you learn this Ability, you gain the Elemental Attunement Lesson once.<br />You may only choose elements that you have the corresponding Elemental Attunement to when using this Ability.<br />Scaling: At any Hero Tier, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 3 to MP increase its damage multiplier by 1.<br />At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by an additional 5 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: This represents a variety of basic elemental attacks. This could be a low level incantation, a jolt of heat vision, launching an icicle from a cryo-gun, firing a taser, using elemental powers to from a rock spike beneath the target, focusing light into a beam with reflective scales, lashing out with one’s shadow, and similar attacks.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Fire/Ice/Earth/Sky/Light/Dark)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668393503284,"modifiedTime":1670974920892,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"h3iXiWNQ4u1sFZ1S","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"q