{"name":"Flash","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-blue-yellow.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: 0<br />Cooldown: 3 rounds<br />Effect: If you hit with this Ability, the target is Blind for 1 round. If you score a Critical Hit the Blindness lasts for 2 rounds. You may choose to use this ability as an Attack (in which case you use Physical Offense and target Physical Defense) or as a Spell (in which case you use Mental Offense and target Mental Defense).<br />Description: A maneuver that temporarily blinds the target. This could be blowing smoke into their eyes, throwing up sand, a blast of light, forcing your shadow into their eyes, or something similar.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"short"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":4},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: 0","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":3,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668447890226,"modifiedTime":1670974920899,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"hfM7LNaKzGzyKHHS","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Psychic Lance","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-large-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: This Spell damages MP instead of HP.</p><p>Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 8 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: You assault a foe's mind. This can represent invoking a spell to cause fear, psychically draining the target, firing a brain scrambling beam, or something similar.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":4},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Special)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668465957615,"modifiedTime":1670974920914,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"juMunsxecjVEMoKA","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Suplex","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/unarmed-punch-fist-yellow-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x2 (Physical)<br />Effect: This Attack may only be used on a target you have Grabbed.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 6 HP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: Striking foes while you have the upper hand in a grappling match. This can be a suplex, a joint lock, slamming their head against the floor, or something similarly brutal that works only while the victim is controlled in a grapple.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":"Enemy is Grabbed"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"hp","target":"attributes.hp.value","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x2 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Grapple"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466631288,"modifiedTime":1670974920925,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"mWHgBLAOwXxdPm60","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Healing Word","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/cross-area-circle-green-white.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Auxiliary [Healing] [Careful]<br />Action: Major<br />Prerequisites: None<br />Range: Medium (Careful: Long)<br />Targets: 1 Ally<br />Cost: 2 MP<br />Effect: The target regains HP equal to a die roll.<br />If you also use your Minor action, increase the MP cost by 1, then add another die to the amount healed.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 6 MP to increase the number of dice healed by 1. This is a total of 2 dice of healing normally, or 3 dice of healing with the Careful action. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A basic healing ability done at a distance. This can represent shouting encouraging words, throwing or launching a syringe filled with a medical concoction, channeling life energy into a target to restore their vitality, and other restorative methods.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["d10","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"#{VERSION}#","coreVersion":"10.303","createdTime":1668465492361,"modifiedTime":1692733849918,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"meD2u9SK4Ivdsr7C","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Snipe","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/targeting/crosshair-scope-sniper-green.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: This Attack has Boon +3. You cannot use this Attack on a round where you have moved. This Attack causes you to be Rooted until your next Turn.<br />Special: This Ability has a minimum Range of Medium; targets who are standing 3 Squares or closer are not valid targets for this Ability.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 7 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A precise ranged attack. This attack involves standing still and taking precise aim, so it is less likely to miss.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"extreme"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":6},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x2 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Shoot"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466586088,"modifiedTime":1670974920925,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"nFjO0O3bqL4xfRnI","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Riposte","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/swords-parry-block-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Damage: x1 (Physical)<br />Effect: You may use your Physical Defense Bonus in place of your Physical Offense when using this Ability.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 5 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A basic counterattack. This could consist of quickly striking foes who miss, setting up a static field around yourself, invoking a divine chant that punishes attackers, parrying blows in a way that depletes your foes’ endurance, and similar ways to counter attack.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"counter","cost":0,"condition":"Targeting Enemy Fails Offense Attempt"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"melee"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466141586,"modifiedTime":1670974920918,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"ot6KhNaE3zJPlEcU","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Aim","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/targeting/crosshair-bars-yellow.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: You make your next attack this round with Boon +2.<br />Description: Taking a moment to steady your aim. This could just be standard careful aim, looking through a scope, activating a targeting system, or other similar actions.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"minor","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"none"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"aux","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668392843714,"modifiedTime":1670974920879,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"paDmOvV4PFuHKRsn","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Kinetic Force","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/ranged/projectile-strike-egg-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: If this Spell scores a Solid Hit and the target is not otherwise restrained, you move them one Square.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 7 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: This can represent telekinetically picking a target up and throwing them a short distance, a wave of psychic energy that knocks the target stumbling backwards, utilizing a gravity gun, whipping up a powerful burst of wind with one’s wings, and similar displacement attacks.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x1 (Physical)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668465667707,"modifiedTime":1670974920910,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"pbm5bzxHI8KpXrJv","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Void Lance","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/unholy/projectile-bolts-salvo-pink.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 15 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A costly way to do high damage. This could be utilizing a forbidden spell, firing an anti-matter weapon, eldritch energy, or similar sources of powerful damage.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"long"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":15},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x3 (Almighty)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Capacity 1"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466906176,"modifiedTime":1670974920932,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"qg926BvlX2skOhwd","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Void Shot","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/unholy/projectile-bullet-orb-pink.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: Using this Attack consumes your Charge Advantage. You cannot use this Attack if you are not Charged.<br />Scaling: At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by 7 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: Attacking with an extremely powerful projectile after preparing. This could represent the release of a powerful experimental firearm, launching powerful ki bullets, or similar attacks.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":"Charge"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"long"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":6},"ability":null,"actionType":"attack","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: x3 (Almighty)","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":"Charge Up & Shoot"},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.5.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668466985177,"modifiedTime":1670974920933,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"_id":"qoV2xMi2mfltFJqu","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3}}
{"name":"Expose","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-purple.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Effect: If you hit, the target decreases on the Defensive Track.<br />You may use this either as an Attack (using your Physical Offense and targeting your opponent’s Physical Defense) or a Spell (using your Mental Offense to target you’re opponent’s Mental Defense).<br />Scaling: At any Hero Tier, you may increase the cost of the Ability by 5 MP to give it a damage multiplier of 1.<br />At Hero Tier 2, you may increase the cost of this Ability by an additional 7 MP to increase its damage multiplier by 1. When used this way, this Ability counts as a Tier 2 Ability.<br />Description: A simple ability to make a target less effective defensively. This could be a curse, distracting or discouraging the target, muddling their mind temporary with telepathic influence, temporarily magnetizing them so attacks are subtly attracted to them, and other things to hinder the target.</p>","chat":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"major","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"medium"},"upkeep":{"type":"","label":"","target":null,"amount":null},"consume":{"type":"attribute","label":"mp","target":"attributes.mp.value","amount":2},"ability":null,"actionType":"spell","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"Damage: 0","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","tier":1,"type":"","careful":false,"prerequisite":"","element":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"requirements":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.jtiBta2FTnxYLEot"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"shaper","systemVersion":"0.1.7.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1668393703003,"modifiedTime":1672693548135,"lastModifiedBy":"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"qMfscaKa4lVUOM7h":3},"_id":